Package org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto

Class SclDTO

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.dto.SclDTO
public class SclDTO extends Object
A representation of the model object SCL.

The following features are supported:

  • Id
  • Version
  • Revision
  • Refers To Header
